INSERT INTO `chatmessages` VALUES (1,1,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-02-07 18:43:40'),(2,2,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-02-07 18:44:08'),(3,2,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor starters:\n1.  Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind? (e.g., Toyota, Hyundai, Kia, BMW, Mercedes, etc.)\n2.  What\'s your approximate **budget range**?\n3.  Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and if used, what **year range** are you considering?\n4.  How many **seats** do you typically need (5 or 7-seater)?\n\nOnce I have this, I can start narrowing down the options!',NULL,'2026-02-07 18:44:13'),(30001,30001,'user','I\'m looking for a new Mercedes c-class',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:50:41'),(30002,30001,'assistant','Ah, the Mercedes C-Class! An excellent choice, known for its luxury and performance.\n\nTo help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\n1.  **What year range** are you considering? (e.g., 2018-2023)\n2.  Are you looking for a **sedan, coupe, or convertible**?\n3.  What\'s your **budget range** for this car?\n4.  Do you have any specific **color preferences**?\n5.  And finally, what will be the **primary use** for the car? (e.g., daily commute, family car, weekend drives)\n\nOnce I have this, I can check our inventory for the best matches!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:50:46'),(30003,30001,'user','Show me luxury sedans from 2017 or newer',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:51:32'),(30004,30001,'assistant','Okay, broadening our search to luxury sedans from 2017 or newer! That opens up a fantastic range of options.\n\nTo help me narrow it down further and find the best fit for you, could you please tell me:\n\n1.  Do you have any **specific brands** in mind besides Mercedes (e.g., BMW, Audi, Lexus, etc.)?\n2.  What\'s your **budget range** for this luxury sedan?\n3.  Are there any **color preferences** you have?\n4.  And what will be the **primary use** for the car? (e.g., daily commute, family car, weekend drives)\n\nOnce I have these details, I can show you some excellent choices from our inventory!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:51:37'),(30005,30001,'user','BMW',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:51:45'),(30006,30001,'assistant','Great! BMW is another fantastic choice for luxury sedans.\n\nSo, we\'re looking for a **BMW luxury sedan, 2017 or newer**.\n\nTo refine this further, could you please tell me:\n\n1.  What\'s your **budget range** for this BMW sedan?\n2.  Do you have any **specific color preferences**?\n3.  And what will be the **primary use** for the car? (e.g., daily commute, family car, weekend drives)\n\nOnce I have these details, I can check our current inventory for available BMW luxury sedans that match your criteria!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:51:49'),(30007,30001,'user','black',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:51:58'),(30008,30001,'assistant','Got it! A **black BMW luxury sedan, 2017 or newer**. That\'s a classic and stylish combination!\n\nTo help me find the perfect one for you, just two more quick questions:\n\n1.  What\'s your **budget range** for this car?\n2.  And what will be the **primary use** for the car? (e.g., daily commute, family car, weekend drives)\n\nOnce I have these, I\'ll dive into our inventory and see what black BMW sedans we have that fit your needs!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:52:02'),(30009,30001,'user','20k budget for a daily used car',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:52:17'),(30010,30001,'assistant','Okay, a **black BMW luxury sedan, 2017 or newer, for daily use, with a budget of $20,000.**\n\nThat\'s a very clear picture!\n\nGiven the criteria of a 2017 or newer BMW luxury sedan, a $20,000 budget might be quite challenging to meet, especially for models typically found in the Lebanese market. Luxury sedans from 2017 onwards, even used, generally start at a higher price point.\n\nWould you be open to:\n1.  **Considering an older model year** (e.g., 2014-2016) to stay within the $20k budget for a BMW luxury sedan?\n2.  **Slightly increasing your budget** to accommodate a 2017+ model?\n3.  **Exploring other luxury brands** that might offer 2017+ sedans closer to the $20k mark?\n\nLet me know what you think, and I\'ll do my best to find some great options for you!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:52:23'),(30011,30001,'user','thanks',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:52:35'),(30012,30001,'assistant','You\'re welcome!\n\nSo, regarding the black BMW luxury sedan for daily use:\n\nGiven that a **2017 or newer BMW luxury sedan** is generally above the **$20,000 budget** in our market, which of these options would you prefer to explore?\n\n1.  **Considering an older model year** (e.g., 2014-2016) to stay within the $20k budget for a BMW luxury sedan?\n2.  **Slightly increasing your budget** to accommodate a 2017+ model?\n3.  **Exploring other luxury brands** that might offer 2017+ sedans closer to the $20k mark?\n\nLet me know which direction you\'d like to go, and I\'ll check our inventory accordingly!',NULL,'2026-02-07 19:52:40'),(60001,60001,'user','I want a good reliable car as my first car. what do you recommend',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:02:25'),(60002,60001,'assistant','That\'s exciting! Getting your first car is a big step. To help me recommend the perfect reliable car for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands or models** in mind, or any you\'d prefer to avoid?\n*   What **type of car** are you thinking of – a compact sedan, a small SUV, something else?\n*   What\'s your approximate **budget range**?\n*   And how will you primarily be using the car – for daily commutes, family, weekend trips, etc.?\n\nOnce I have a better idea, I can help you find some great options!',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:02:30'),(60003,60001,'user','mercedes c300',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:03:14'),(60004,60001,'assistant','Ah, the Mercedes C300! Excellent choice – known for its blend of luxury, performance, and reliability.\n\nTo help me narrow down the perfect C300 for you, could you also tell me:\n\n*   What **year range** are you considering for the C300?\n*   Do you have any **color preferences**?\n*   What\'s your approximate **budget range** for this car?\n*   And how will you primarily be **using the car** – for daily commutes, city driving, longer trips, etc.?\n\nOnce I have these details, I can check our current inventory for available Mercedes C300 models that match your criteria!',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:03:18'),(60005,60001,'user','my budget is 17000 usd',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:03:38'),(60006,60001,'assistant','Okay, $17,000 USD is a clear budget. That\'s helpful!\n\nConsidering a Mercedes C300 with that budget, we\'ll likely be looking at slightly older models, which can still be fantastic and reliable cars.\n\nTo refine our search further for a C300 that fits your budget, could you also tell me:\n\n*   What **year range** are you hoping for?\n*   Do you have any **color preferences**?\n*   And how will you primarily be **using the car** – for daily commutes, city driving, longer trips, etc.?\n\nOnce I have these details, I can check our inventory for available Mercedes C300s within your budget and preferences!',NULL,'2026-02-09 18:03:43'),(90001,90001,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-02-17 00:22:37'),(90002,90001,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your **budget range** for the car?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you prefer?\n*   How many **seats** do you typically need (5-seater, 7-seater)?\n*   Any specific **colors** you like or dislike?\n\nOnce I have a better idea, I can start filtering our inventory for you!',NULL,'2026-02-17 00:22:41'),(90003,90002,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-02-17 00:23:01'),(90004,90002,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   What\'s your estimated budget range?\n*   Are there any specific brands or models you prefer, or perhaps ones you\'d like to avoid?\n*   Do you have a preferred year range in mind?\n*   How many seats do you need (5-seater, 7-seater)?',NULL,'2026-02-17 00:23:06'),(120001,120001,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:36:07'),(120002,120001,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\n1.  Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n2.  What\'s your **budget range** for the car?\n3.  Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and if used, what **year range** are you considering?\n4.  Are there any specific **features** important for your family, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or advanced safety?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:36:12'),(120003,120002,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:36:40'),(120004,120002,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands** or **models** in mind?\n*   What **year range** are you considering?\n*   What\'s your preferred **budget range**?\n*   Are there any specific **features** important for your family, like 3 rows of seats, a large trunk, or fuel efficiency?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:36:44'),(120005,120003,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:08'),(120006,120003,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor starters, do you have any **preferred brands** in mind, or a **budget range**? Also, how many people will typically be riding in the SUV, and what **year range** are you considering?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:11'),(120007,120004,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:23'),(120008,120004,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your approximate **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you prefer?\n*   How many **seats** do you need (5-seater, 7-seater)?\n*   Any specific **features** that are important for your family, like safety, fuel efficiency, or cargo space?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:27'),(120009,120005,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:41'),(120010,120005,'assistant','Ah, a family SUV! That\'s a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands or specific models** in mind?\n*   What **year range** are you considering?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget**?\n*   Are there any particular **features** important for your family, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or specific safety options?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:37:45'),(120011,120006,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:38:06'),(120012,120006,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a popular choice for its versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your **budget range** for the car?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you prefer?\n*   How many **seats** do you need (5-seater, 7-seater)?\n*   Are there any other features important to your family, like **fuel efficiency** or specific **safety features**?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:38:10'),(120013,120007,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:49:10'),(120014,120007,'assistant','That\'s a great choice for Lebanon! Family SUVs are very popular here.\n\nTo help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\n*   Do you have any **brands** in mind, like Toyota, Kia, Hyundai, or something else?\n*   What\'s your preferred **budget range** for the car?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and if used, what **year range** are you considering?\n*   And finally, are there any specific **features** important for your family, like 7 seats, good fuel economy, or advanced safety features?',NULL,'2026-03-07 01:49:15'),(150001,150001,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:12:23'),(150002,150001,'assistant','Great choice! A family SUV is perfect for our Lebanese roads and lifestyles. To help me find the best options for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\n1.  Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n2.  What\'s your **budget range** for this SUV?\n3.  Are you looking for a **new or used** car, and if used, what **year range** are you considering?\n4.  Are there any specific features important for your family, like **7 seats**, good **fuel efficiency**, or advanced **safety features**?\n\nOnce I have a better idea, I can start looking through our inventory!',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:12:29'),(150003,150002,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:13:11'),(150004,150002,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a popular choice for its versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any preferred **brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you prefer?\n*   Are there any specific **features** that are important for your family, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or cargo space?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:13:17'),(150005,150003,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:14:45'),(150006,150003,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a popular choice for its versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands** in mind (e.g., Toyota, Hyundai, Mercedes)?\n*   What\'s your preferred **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you consider?\n*   Any specific **features** important for your family, like 7-seater capacity, fuel efficiency, or advanced safety features?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:14:51'),(150007,150004,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:15:37'),(150008,150004,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your ideal **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** SUV, and what **year range** would you prefer?\n*   How many **seats** do you typically need (5-seater, 7-seater)?\n*   Any specific **features** that are important for your family, like safety, fuel efficiency, or a big trunk?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:15:43'),(150009,150005,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:16:02'),(150010,150005,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands** in mind, or perhaps any **models** you like?\n*   What **year range** are you considering?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget range**?\n*   Are there any specific **colors** you prefer or dislike?\n*   And thinking about your family, will you need a **3rd row** of seating, or is a 5-seater sufficient?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:16:08'),(150011,150006,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:17:40'),(150012,150006,'assistant','That\'s great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me narrow down the options from our inventory, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **newer model** or something a bit older?\n*   And for a family SUV, are things like **7-seater capacity**, **fuel efficiency**, or **luxury features** particularly important to you?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:17:44'),(150013,150007,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:32:50'),(150014,150007,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for Lebanon\'s roads and for accommodating everyone comfortably.\n\nTo help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\n1.  Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n2.  What\'s your approximate **budget range**?\n3.  Are you looking for a **new or pre-owned** SUV, and if pre-owned, what **year range** are you considering?\n4.  Are there any specific **features important for your family**, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or advanced safety features?',NULL,'2026-03-11 15:32:55'),(180001,180001,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:15:30'),(180002,180001,'assistant','Ah, a family SUV! That\'s a popular choice in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor a family SUV, it\'s often helpful to know:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** in mind?\n*   What\'s your approximate **budget range**?\n*   Are you looking for a **new or used** car, and if used, what **year range** are you considering?\n*   Any specific **features** that are important for your family, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or safety tech?',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:15:34'),(180003,180002,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:20:02'),(180004,180002,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a fantastic choice for versatility and space. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **preferred brands** or **models** in mind?\n*   What **year range** are you considering?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget range**?\n*   How many **seats** do you typically need (5-seater, 7-seater)?\n*   Any particular **colors** you like or dislike?\n\nThe more details you share, the better I can narrow down the options!',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:20:06'),(180005,180003,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:22:06'),(180006,180003,'assistant','Ah, a family SUV! That\'s a popular choice here in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example:\n*   Do you have any **brands or models** in mind?\n*   What **year range** are you considering?\n*   What\'s your estimated **budget**?\n*   Are there any specific **features** important for your family, like 7 seats, fuel efficiency, or specific safety options?',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:22:10'),(180007,180004,'user','I\'m looking for a family SUV',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:52:23'),(180008,180004,'assistant','Great! A family SUV is a popular choice in Lebanon. To help me find the perfect one for you, could you tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor a family SUV, it\'s really helpful to know:\n\n1.  **What\'s your estimated budget range?** (e.g., $15,000 - $25,000)\n2.  **Are there any specific brands or models you prefer or dislike?**\n3.  **What year range are you considering?** (e.g., 2018 or newer)\n4.  **How many seats do you need?** (5-seater or 7-seater?)\n5.  **Any color preferences?**\n\nOnce I have a better idea, I can check our inventory for some great options!',NULL,'2026-03-16 19:52:28');
